- [Carlo] Stinky.

56:03.000 --> 56:03.458
- What's funny?

56:05.291 --> 56:06.458
- Nothing, Mom.

56:07.834 --> 56:09.291
- Is that my bottle?

56:09.291 --> 56:10.000
- [Carlo] You want some?

56:10.000 --> 56:12.000
- [Mom] Okay.

56:12.000 --> 56:13.250
21?

56:13.250 --> 56:14.875
- [Carlo] You down?

56:15.333 --> 56:16.792
Let's play.

56:19.333 --> 56:22.041
- [Mom] You know what
they call a card dispenser

56:22.041 --> 56:23.166
in a casino?

56:24.125 --> 56:25.000
- What?

56:26.291 --> 56:27.625
- A Shoe.

56:27.625 --> 56:29.041
Isn't that funny?

56:31.125 --> 56:34.291
I like to feel them
though, the cards.

56:35.417 --> 56:36.500
More personal.

56:44.250 --> 56:44.667
- [Scott] Shit.

56:47.125 --> 56:48.625
- I think he bust.

56:52.250 --> 56:53.041
- Fuck.

56:53.041 --> 56:54.125
- I'll stay.

57:01.041 --> 57:03.333
- Flip 'em honey.

57:04.959 --> 57:06.083
(chuckling)

57:06.083 --> 57:08.542
- Push.

57:08.542 --> 57:09.417
- Push.

57:11.709 --> 57:16.917
Sometimes it's good not
to be personal, though.

57:16.917 --> 57:17.625
You get me?

57:19.834 --> 57:22.417
With the folks, they deal too.

57:22.417 --> 57:25.750
Sometimes I feel
like the Grim Reaper.

57:25.750 --> 57:28.583
Ruining all those
lives, those men.

57:29.792 --> 57:32.417
Betting money they don't
have or hope to have

57:32.417 --> 57:32.667
or never had.

57:35.667 --> 57:39.500
And I just sit there
smiling at them.

57:39.500 --> 57:41.917
Made me stop going to church.

57:44.083 --> 57:46.083
- I didn't know that.

57:46.083 --> 57:47.250
- Why?

57:47.250 --> 57:49.166
- It's too many sins.

57:49.166 --> 57:50.917
I mean...

57:50.917 --> 57:52.792
Gambling is a sin, fine.

57:53.959 --> 57:54.834
But...

57:56.667 --> 57:56.792
